OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FThe state's official forecaster will
OL,7,Falso lay out its key projections over
OL,8,Fhow the economy is set to fare over
OL,9,Fthe coming years, with fears that it
OL,10,Fcould present a gloomy outlook in the
OL,11,Fshort term.
OL,13,FHere the PA news agency looks at the
OL,14,Fimportance of this Budget for the
OL,15,Feconomy:
