OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FThe UK economy started the year with
OL,7,Fpositive growth, with GDP (gross
OL,8,Fdomestic product) rising by around
OL,9,F0.7% over the first quarter of the
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FNevertheless, this had been boosted by
OL,13,Fstronger trade ahead of expected
OL,14,Ftariffs and came amid an increasingly
OL,15,Funcertain global economic backdrop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
