OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FThis growth has steadily slowed down
OL,7,Fas the year progressed, with the
OL,8,FOffice for National Statistics (ONS)
OL,9,Freporting growth of 0.3% in the second
OL,10,Fquarter and 0.1% in the third quarter
OL,11,Fof the year.
OL,13,FThe dip has come amid declines in the
OL,14,Fproduction sector as well as slower
OL,15,Fgrowth in the services sector.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, inflation has been elevated
OL,18,Fover the past year, striking a peak of
OL,19,F3.8% in July, August and September.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
