OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FIt dipped slightly last month `
OL,7,Falthough at a slower rate than
OL,8,Fexpected ` but also comes amid a
OL,9,Fbackdrop of falling wage growth.
OL,11,FConsumer finances had been supported
OL,12,Fby stronger wages but real wage growth
OL,13,Fhas slowed significantly in recent
OL,14,Fmonths because of pressure in the
OL,15,Flabour market.
OL,17,FUnemployment has also lifted, striking
OL,18,Fa four-year-high of 5% in the three
OL,19,Fmonths to September.
