OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FWeak hiring, slowing wage growth and
OL,7,Fprice inflation have all been partly
OL,8,Flinked to policies which came into
OL,9,Fforce following the Labour
OL,10,FGovernment's first budget last year.
OL,12,FThe budget led to higher taxes and
OL,13,Flabour costs for many businesses when
OL,14,Fthe policies came into force in April
OL,15,Fthis year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
