OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FBusinesses and trade bodies have
OL,7,Fstressed that they came under pressure
OL,8,Ffrom the previous budget and have
OL,9,Furged the Government to avoid hitting
OL,10,Fthem with further increases.
OL,12,FIndustry data has also shown that some
OL,13,Fbusiness spending has been held back
OL,14,Fahead of the Budget, with firms
OL,15,Fcautious about their financial
OL,16,Fposition.
