OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FThe latest monthly flash PMI economic
OL,7,Fdata ` which shows activity in the
OL,8,FUK's private sector ` showed that
OL,9,Factivity was dented by cautious
OL,10,Fdecision making from firms before the
OL,11,FBudget.
OL,13,F` What is the view of consumers?
OL,15,FConsumer spending has also been
OL,16,Fbroadly cautious in recent months,
OL,17,Fwith Bank of England policymakers
OL,18,Frecently highlighting a focus on
OL,19,Fsaving in favour of spending.
