OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FOn Friday, the ONS said retail sales
OL,7,Fcontracted in October for the first
OL,8,Ftime in three months as shoppers also
OL,9,Fheld off before the Budget.
OL,11,FEconomists have cautioned that
OL,12,Fpredicted rises in personal taxes at
OL,13,Fthe Budget come mean that some
OL,14,Fconsumers will reduce their spending
OL,15,Fplans rather than just delay them
OL,16,Funtil nearer to Christmas.
