OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FNevertheless, reports have suggested
OL,7,Fthat original predictions of a roughly
OL,8,F#30 billion fiscal hole have now been
OL,9,Freduced, with the Financial Times
OL,10,Findicating the OBR think this will be
OL,11,Fnearer to #20 billion.
OL,13,FLast week, reports indicated the
OL,14,FGovernment would therefore not push
OL,15,Fforward with expected increases to
OL,16,Fincome tax as they did not need to
OL,17,Fraise as much money in order to plug
OL,18,Fthis black hole.
