OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FThe Budget can impact trading in the
OL,7,Ffinancial markets, as has significant
OL,8,Fspeculation about potential policy
OL,9,Fdecisions.
OL,11,FTypically, the value of the pound and
OL,12,Fthe price of gilts ` government bonds
OL,13,F` are the most likely to be influenced
OL,14,Fby budget policy.
OL,16,FGilt yields, which rise as prices
OL,17,Ffall, ticked higher earlier this week
OL,18,Fbut are still significantly lower than
OL,19,Fearlier this year as borrowing costs
OL,20,Fhave drifted lower amid lower interest
OL,21,Frates.
