OL,3,CWhy is this Budget so important for
OL,4,Cthe UK economy?
OL,6,FBoth the pound and gilt prices tend to
OL,7,Freach positively to cautious spending
OL,8,Fcommitments and limited tax changes,
OL,9,Fparticularly if they believe tax
OL,10,Fpolicy is likely to hamper economic
OL,11,Fgrowth or wider investment.
OL,13,FThe FTSE 100 and other domestic equity
OL,14,Findexes do not tend to be directly
OL,15,Fimpacted by changes in domestic
OL,16,Fpolicy, although they can be
OL,17,Finfluenced by fluctuations in the
OL,18,Fpound.
